    ISG, reporting to me.  Dave will be responsible for all 
    ISG-wide marketing activities.  He has had a varied background 
    with McDonnell Douglas and brings a wealth of experience to 
    this position.  Most recently he was Vice President, Corporate 
    Marketing, for the Blue Sector.  Report to Dave are the 
    following:

