      Systems Company, headed by Adnan Elassad, and the 
      McDonnell Douglas Banking Systems Company, under 
      Dick Langford, transfer into the McDonnell Douglas 
      Diversified Information Systems Company, enhancing this 
      company's offerings to Banking and Financial institutions.

