Information Systems Company along two lines:

  1)  The sales force will sell systems and services directly to 
      corporations that are not part of the customer and prospect 
      classifications specifically assigned to vertical industry 
      companies.







  2)  The following businesses will sell their products through 
      both the McDonnell Douglas Diversified Information Systems 
