         amount of support.  The acquiring business units 
         recognize the need for continued cost-effective support 
         services to other business units.  All business units are 
         encouraged to continue to use these resources.

    5)   Library and Guest Services have become part of a 
         St. Louis Metropolitan Services organization reporting to 
         Ed Hamilton, Director - Special Projects.

