       acquisition  cost  of  more  than  $1000  per item require
       approval  of  the  applicable  ISG Company Head (Component
       Head),  coordination  with  the Corporate Vice President -
       ISG  Finance,  and  the  approval  of  the  Corporate Vice
       President - Civic Affairs.

