contributions  of  this  nature,  these items are to be listed on
the  applicable  property  disposition  authority document by the
disposing  company's  property  inventory  control  manager  with
concurrence of the company controller.

For  those items having an original acquisition cost of more than
$1000,  the  property  disposition authority document bearing the
approval  of  the  disposing  Company  Head is to be submitted to
Inventory  and  Data Control in ISG Procurement.  This department
will  coordinate  the request with the Corporate Vice President -
ISG  Finance,  and  submit  it  to the Corporate Vice President -
Civic  Affairs  for  approval.    Inventory and Data Control will
return the approved document to the originating company.

